app_description: All language Super Translate lets you feel comfortable while chatting working with peoples in other languages. You can avail yourself of Super Translate Dictionary by installing it to your mobile for chatting with people from numerous countries with different languages. Features Of Super Translate Translate words Texts and Sentences Simple User Interface Easy to use for Translation Helps to learn New language for everyone Text to speech function Text Translator for all languages Edit your translations and copy and share Save translations to your phone Translate save Use history tab to save translations. You can save your translate content in history. Go to translator screen translate any text tap on the star and save translation. All Language Translator Free. Use all languages translator app speak to translate feature to translate words from any language to any local language. Text translator all languages This free all languages translator app also features text to voice translator. Language Translator Free Text Translate All languages is an easy and free translator app. You can translate and speak any language with speech translate feature of Super Translate app. Following languages are Supported for Translation in Super Translate Afrikaans Albanians Amharic Arabic Armenian Azerbaijani Basque Belarusian Bengali Bosnian Bulgarian Catalan Chichewa Chinese Corsican Croatian Czech Danish Dutch English Esperanto Estonian Filipino Finnish French Frisian Galician Georgian German Greek Gujarati Haitian Creole Hausa Hebrew Hindi Hungarian Icelandic Igbo Indonesian Irish Italian Japanese Javanese Kannada Kazakh Khmer Korean Kurdish Kurmanji Kyrgyz Latvian Latviešu Lithuanian Lietuvių Malagasy Malay Melayu Maltese Il Malti Norwegian Norsk Persian فارسی Polish Polski Portuguese Português Querétaro Otomi Romanian Română Russian Русский Samoan Serbian Cyrillic Cрпски ћирилица Serbian Latin Srpski latinica Slovak Slovenčina Slovenian Slovenščina Spanish Español Swahili Kiswahili Swedish Svenska Tajik Tamil Telugu Thai Turkish Ukrainian Urdu Uzbek Vietnamese Welsh Xhosa Yiddish Yoruba Zulu We provide 1 month 3.99 3 month 7.99 1 year 29.99 subscription plan please pay attention to the following tips when you make purchase 1.
